        <div>
          <Intro>I help organizations build better digital products.</Intro>
        </div>

        <div id="engagements">
          <p>
            As a designer, developer and founder with a strategic mindset and
            in-depth expertise in digital product development, I have led
            cross-functional teams, built sustainable organisational structures
